{"tid":686490,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"補習每月補成5000蚊","createTime":"2018-06-01T10:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T10:41:45.000Z","uid":109356,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4efba79afb2d770333bf05bf7587d65622e47f","tid":686490,"uid":109356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"話説我有個同學 認為學校係垃圾，從來唔做學校嘅功課同test，然後佢每月交成4至5000遵理補習，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補全科同私補英文。<br />\n<br />\n佢淨係做補習嘅野，唔會聽書，上中文温通識。每日瞓2個鐘 ，其餘時間全部温書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁極端有冇可能入到GBUS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdda55a27831f025d25eb284736b10172131070","tid":686490,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"冇自信咪會咁"},{"pid":"81bb033bd3480ddb8c02c697a7e73c9c7d7085c5","tid":686490,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗補全科呀 全科都垃圾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9e2204d4b3c36c9a33a65c4863515d2aa15968","tid":686490,"uid":146185,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"同我當年好似 又係aim GBUS唔理學校教既野，教補習<br />\n日校老師的確大部份垃圾，補習搵啱好老師既話會識得點讀果科<br />\n<br />\n中六補中英通識<br />\n數&amp;phychembio靠自己操卷，呢幾科我覺得係content based subjects, 冇乜skills&amp;思維可言，功力全靠自己操pastpaper<br />\n<br />\naim GBUS最後入左hku BBA(Law) <br />\n比你個friend 參考"},{"pid":"8bb109b0aa39f3e02026efb8782b83e5f4bbf208","tid":686490,"uid":50926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:26:21.000Z","msg":"利申 試過，最後4科5**同3科4<br />\n<br />\n我覺得作用唔大，勁果堆嘅人中三四已經爆緊seed，補習係提供一個方法比你。最重要係自己有冇時間同肯唔肯溫書，識人唔洗補習都6科5**入medic"},{"pid":"085df7667a4d43c5c582b56edb6958761734c198","tid":686490,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"一睇佢話每日瞓兩粒鐘就知吹水啦"}]}